<h1 id="introduction">Introduction</h1>
<p>Although a terminal emulator is synonymous with a shell or text terminal, the terminal includes all remote terminals, including graphical interfaces.</p>

<p>A terminal emulator within a graphical user interface is often called a terminal window.</p>

<hr />

<h1 id="ranking">Ranking</h1>
<p>Now letâ€™s go to the ranking I created with a summary of each one!</p>

