<h1 id="9Âº-tmux">9Âº <a href="https://github.com/tmux/tmux">Tmux</a></h1>
<p><img src="/assets/img/terminal/tmux.jpg" alt="TMUX" /></p>

<p><a href="https://github.com/tmux/tmux">Tmux</a> is software that serves to multiplex multiple terminals, allowing a user to access multiple separate terminal sessions within a single terminal window or remote terminal session. It is useful for handling multiple programs. There are some similar applications like: GNU Screen, Byobu, Wemux, among others.</p>

