<h1 id="6Âº-terminology">6Âº <a href="https://www.enlightenment.org/about-terminology.md">Terminology</a></h1>
<p><img src="/assets/img/terminal/terminology.png" alt="Terminology" /></p>

<p>Terminology is a terminal emulator for Linux/BSD/UNIX systems that uses the EFL library. It is part of the Desktop Environment Enlightenment.</p>

<p>Terminology official address: <a href="https://www.enlightenment.org/about-terminology.md">https://www.enlightenment.org/about-terminology.md</a></p>

<hr />

<h1 id="5Âº-hyper">5Âº <a href="https://hyper.is/">Hyper</a></h1>
<p><img src="/assets/img/terminal/hyper.png" alt="Hyper" /></p>

<p><a href="https://hyper.is/">Hyper</a> is a modern proposal for terminal emulators.</p>

